{"tid":1016854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國廉航Jet2因無水沖茶咖啡改道降落　乘客斥：假期開始前已被毀掉","createTime":"2019-02-11T04:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T06:09:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f5ee05ef375dce3c8a5cfe482a1e1fa0a87976","tid":1016854,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190211/s00005/894c5a010393865c65ada8fa6614670a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190211%2Fs00005%2F894c5a010393865c65ada8fa6614670a.jpg&h=5d50bf37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國廉航Jet2周日（10日）一架往西班牙特內里費島（Tenerife）的航班，因機上欠缺熱水沖製茶和咖啡，需要改道於曼徹斯特降落；不少乘客不滿，斥其「假期在開始前已被毀掉」。<br />\n<br />\nJet2一架LS155航班，原定由蘇格蘭格拉斯哥（Glasgow）飛往特內里費島，飛至愛爾蘭南部科克市（Cork）改道，於曼徹斯特降落，當時還有消防人員在場戒備。<br />\n<br />\nJet2發言人解釋，航班出現技術問題，未能提供熱水沖製茶和咖啡；航班乘客在曼徹斯特機場轉乘另一架機前往特內里費島。<br />\n<br />\n此事令乘客大感不滿，有人質疑飛機改道降落原因竟是無法提供熱飲，「Jet2下次找個好些的藉口吧」；有人抱怨「假期在開始前已被毀掉，兒子們在哭，『多謝』」。<br />\n<br />\n（鏡報／英國廣播公司）"},{"pid":"10ee6c516ef878a777e3d2221320ae6f287be6d8","tid":1016854,"uid":63303,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"飛機水缸污糟到爆，有得飲都咪撚飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00eda69dc201b10d2ba5d2ee90929370af3f383","tid":1016854,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"10ee6c516ef878a777e3d2221320ae6f287be6d8","tid":1016854,"uid":63303,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"飛機水缸污糟到爆，有得飲都咪撚飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"樽裝水<br />\n<br />\n利申: ex係空姐"},{"pid":"658490da0d3999a5f7d0de8c86feb5e26ac12c97","tid":1016854,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"10ee6c516ef878a777e3d2221320ae6f287be6d8","tid":1016854,"uid":63303,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"飛機水缸污糟到爆，有得飲都咪撚飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"但杯面 沖嘅飲品就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd306b0d38433f6d8d853074d63cbbc679b0c693","tid":1016854,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:11:41.000Z","msg":"無錢又要咁多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a717a169a277ba23acdf62a85cc94228978a33","tid":1016854,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"應該係啲閪客屌佢地冇熱水<br />\n機師嬲嬲地攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a04e59f58e66b43242032a95014b16776d2ca74","tid":1016854,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:55:09.000Z","msg":"似大鑊野 想隱瞞"},{"pid":"44e987057d376640011c16917364eaff00726c11","tid":1016854,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T06:09:26.000Z","msg":"籍口黎<br />\n應該係見到ufo"}]}